to create a C# Azure Function first install the tools:
dotnet new -i Microsoft.Azure.WebJobs.ProjectTemplates
to install func so you can create the function with templates
npm install -g azure-functions-core-tools@4 --unsafe-perm true 
create the function 
dotnet new func -n CPTestFunctionApp -o CPTestFunctionApp
add file : TestHttpFunction.cs and 


***To create the database using terraform:
Install azure CLI in your machine
login to your Azure account : 
az login   #use your credentials
locate in the Infrastructure folder and execute:
terraform init
terraform plan
terraform apply
